testCase.name: CreateTenantService should be able create a tenant with a valid name
CreateTenantService should not be able create a tenant with a already existing one
ListTenantService should be able to list a tenant with a valid id
ListTenantService should not be able to list a tenant with a invalid id
UpdateTenantService should be able to update a existing tenant
UpdateTenantService should not update a non existing tenant
UpdateTenantService should not be able to update a tenant's name to a already existing one
ListAllRolesService should be able to list all roles
ListTenantService should be able to list a role with a valid id
ListTenantService should not be able to list a role with a invalid id
